snippet.title: Devil of the Mirror - ALL ENDINGS (RPG Maker Horror)
snippet.description:
Devil of the Mirror (鏡ノ悪魔) - a short puzzle/horror game made by Tokiiro Kaeru (時彩 蛙) in the year of 2017. This video contains all endings, including the true ending. 

Thumbnail Artwork by the creator of the game, available on their twitter- frog4151

Synopsis:

Striving to escape her futile existence, a lonely and sick girl is performing a spell upon a mirror, wishing for friends and for a better life... But she didn't know that the mirror she used was holding a demonic entity in it. Will that spell be a blessing for the girl... or a curse?

Chapters:
0:00 The Winding Key
2:33 The Hall of Dolls
16:17 Shuni and Cher
40:17 Return to Grand Guignol 
56:10 Extinguished Candle (End 4)
1:01:43 A Promise That Cannot Be Fulfilled (End 2)  
1:06:54 The Girl Who Became the ...? (True End)
1:20:25 Washu Talks about Devil of the Mirror
